{"tid":1134884,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想問其實搞藝術其實對社會有無貢獻？","createTime":"2019-05-02T03:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T14:52:52.000Z","uid":132030,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c149f245010039255292d481b595f7085001f124","tid":1134884,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:25:30.000Z","msg":"大家點睇"},{"pid":"da516fb3072f6a9a7a97978465f7d91cbd0965c5","tid":1134884,"uid":109655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:26:58.000Z","msg":"娛樂大眾"},{"pid":"858e30c1d6de21fe26d4b73da86b9e541f1d1391","tid":1134884,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:27:07.000Z","msg":"連登仔究竟點睇"},{"pid":"2455a37c4e0f8086075f6ddec9b944c9ecd3bb7e","tid":1134884,"uid":76885,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:32:07.000Z","msg":"人既生活要咩？<br />\n物質，衣食住行好就滿足？<br />\n<br />\n感官享受係咩？<br />\n係咪需要靚既野先更享受？<br />\n<br />\n有無見過&hellip;人造&hellip;而靚到令你著迷既野？<br />\n譬如一首感動你既流行曲。<br />\n一座有莊嚴感既建築物。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得明白有人覺得唔重要。<br />\n但我覺得重要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n甚至想像：<br />\n一個只滿足本能欲望既人生，去到75歲死，中間既生活重重複複，係為咩？<br />\n<br />\n如果75年入面，喺精神上得到藝術既滋潤，會唔會覺得生命過得有意義啲？<br />\n<br />\n都覺得明白有人覺得唔重要。<br />\n但我覺得重要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c6353a8089f4a15502fdd0680b0f478e9b5d27","tid":1134884,"uid":45353,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:32:56.000Z","msg":"對資本社會唔重要"},{"pid":"58ea197f8743ca3053ede59de96d60b70746245d","tid":1134884,"uid":10524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"57c6353a8089f4a15502fdd0680b0f478e9b5d27","tid":1134884,"uid":45353,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:32:56.000Z","msg":"對資本社會唔重要"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:34:32.000Z","msg":"痴線 藝術不知幾賺錢 <br />\n大把經濟效益"},{"pid":"fcb1f0a5da6b8035221dd2d89b2a4e507bff40f4","tid":1134884,"uid":45353,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"58ea197f8743ca3053ede59de96d60b70746245d","tid":1134884,"uid":10524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"57c6353a8089f4a15502fdd0680b0f478e9b5d27","tid":1134884,"uid":45353,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:32:56.000Z","msg":"對資本社會唔重要"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:34:32.000Z","msg":"痴線 藝術不知幾賺錢 <br />\n大把經濟效益"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:14:11.000Z","msg":"無效率"},{"pid":"b6da79c2914ea096bb2aac98c6d322f15a0e0508","tid":1134884,"uid":47669,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T05:02:23.000Z","msg":"拍戲算唔算搞藝術？<br />\n<br />\n藝術的確唔係直接令窮人有飯開<br />\n唔可以解決社會民生問題<br />\n但你睇下世界上邊一個成熟嘅社會<br />\n係唔支持發展藝術？<br />\n<br />\n係精神層面嘅追求<br />\n開得呢個post嘅人都係繼續吃喝玩樂啦"},{"pid":"7a58cafe2e874061f36f504c19b65affd507a0d3","tid":1134884,"uid":211579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T05:09:58.000Z","msg":"又係呢d濕尻問題<br />\n<br />\n一件衫，支那藝術家設計vs 日本藝術家設計<br />\n<br />\n你睇下邊件暢銷？點會無貢獻？"},{"pid":"975f6ba3af15ed36acc1d126ae7237444f7d10b0","tid":1134884,"uid":195601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:26:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.researchhistory.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/maslows-hierarchy-of-needs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchhistory.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F06%2Fmaslows-hierarchy-of-needs.gif&h=c77ee748&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMaslow's Hierarchy of Needs<br />\n我認為藝術（無論任何形式）最能夠滿足塔頂嗰兩項"},{"pid":"902872081d5f251312f51765f187d786f9988245","tid":1134884,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:28:40.000Z","msg":"好多movement都係藝術家發起／參與。"},{"pid":"20aa0b8e1728d079bc38a8f77455aeb7af68c211","tid":1134884,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:29:43.000Z","msg":"音樂唔係藝術<br />\n電影唔係藝術"},{"pid":"24dc5b2725d8d2db0e16686f46f19010f3be0395","tid":1134884,"uid":165619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58ea197f8743ca3053ede59de96d60b70746245d","tid":1134884,"uid":10524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"57c6353a8089f4a15502fdd0680b0f478e9b5d27","tid":1134884,"uid":45353,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:32:56.000Z","msg":"對資本社會唔重要"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:34:32.000Z","msg":"痴線 藝術不知幾賺錢 <br />\n大把經濟效益"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:32:52.000Z","msg":"最大嘅經濟效益係要嚟洗乾淨D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb95b4e19450a9e7b4fed011bddfef0eef071e5","tid":1134884,"uid":111768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:51:13.000Z","msg":"藝術即係包含設計, 創意創新, 美感元素啦<br />\n室內設計係藝術 可以令你覺得間屋靚左 住都舒服啲<br />\n<br />\n產品設計係藝術 例如每一件衫褲鞋襪都有佢既搭配美感所在 無人希望所有衫褲都用同一顏色同一logo進行生產 <br />\n<br />\n髮型設計係藝術 頭髮係一個人美感提升最為重要之一 修飾完頭髮你會感到自信 你都唔想好似北韓咁個個整個金正恩頭<br />\n<br />\n語言文字都係藝術 識得溝通技巧好多時可以避免人與人之間有摩擦和衝突 一個人懂得利用語言藝術 起碼比人既第一印象你唔會差 先會令到後話有延伸機會<br />\n<br />\n所以藝術存在於社會每一方面每一層面, 佢可能無科研技術果啲咁明顯令你感受到啲貢獻 但其實科研技術都基於藝術既創新理念. 而且藝術對人精神方面既提升係無可否認, 你睇場戲聽首歌都會令你產生情緒波動, 所以點會無貢獻？"},{"pid":"5f50233175ca1dc3f4bd971155648f827598c7d9","tid":1134884,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24dc5b2725d8d2db0e16686f46f19010f3be0395","tid":1134884,"uid":165619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58ea197f8743ca3053ede59de96d60b70746245d","tid":1134884,"uid":10524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"57c6353a8089f4a15502fdd0680b0f478e9b5d27","tid":1134884,"uid":45353,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:32:56.000Z","msg":"對資本社會唔重要"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:34:32.000Z","msg":"痴線 藝術不知幾賺錢 <br />\n大把經濟效益"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:32:52.000Z","msg":"最大嘅經濟效益係要嚟洗乾淨D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:52:52.000Z","msg":"藝術對旅遊業影響好大"}]}